      <title>法国核能公司称尼日尔军政府接管铀矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/french-nuclear-firm-says-niger-junta-takes-over-uranium-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国奥拉诺公司 (Orano SA) 称，尼日尔已经取得索迈尔铀矿的运营控制权，此举正值法国国家控制的核能集团与非洲国家军政府之间的冲突不断升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/french-nuclear-firm-says-niger-junta-takes-over-uranium-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:19:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受补贴热潮影响，中国 11 月汽车销量有望增长 18%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-november-car-sales-seen-surging-18-on-subsidy-rush</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于汽车制造商加大折扣，且买家争相在政府以旧换新补贴结束前享受补贴，中国 11 月份汽车销量可能大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-november-car-sales-seen-surging-18-on-subsidy-rush</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
